        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 textarea-component">       
            
<div class="text">
<h2>Our Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>This Privacy Policy explains what personal information we have, how we use it and how you can check and update any personal information we have about you.</p>

<p>Watch our video below to learn more about our Privacy Policy.</p>
<!-- Start of Brightcove Player -->

<div style="display:none"> </div>
<iframe allowfullscreen="" mozallowfullscreen="" src="//players.brightcove.net/115368538001/default_default/index.html?videoId=3325337959001" webkitallowfullscreen=""></iframe><!--
